"The United States needs Greenland for the purpose of [national security](https://www.foxnews.com/category/politics/executive/national-security)," Trump wrote in a Truth Social post Wednesday.

He has said Greenland is integral to the [country’s Golden Dome project](https://www.foxnews.com/politics/golden-dome-missile-shield-tested-trump-key-american-territory), a proposed U.S. missile-defense shield. Trump added that if the U.S. does not secure the territory, "Russia or China will" and called on NATO to back U.S. efforts to take control of Greenland.

